                "invention-title": [
                    "Trehalose ester as well as preparation, purification and decolorization method and application thereof",
                    "海藻糖酯及其制备、纯化与脱色方法和应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses trehalose ester. The trehalose ester is a mixture of ester of trehalose and fatty acid, the trehalose ester comprises monoester, diester and triester, the content of monoester is more than 40%, and the highest content can reach 70% or more; the fatty acid can be C6-C24 fatty acid or a mixture thereof, preferably, the content of C12 fatty acid is greater than or equal to 50%, and most preferably, the content of C12 fatty acid is greater than or equal to 70%. A solvent-free method and a transesterification synthesis route are adopted, potassium carbonate and sodium stearate with low toxicity are selected as a catalyst and a dispersing agent, and an ethyl acetate/ethanol separation system and an activated carbon/hydrogen peroxide ethanol decolorization system are combined to develop a high-monoester-content and high-purity monoester. And the industrial low-cost solvent-free preparation method of the trehalose ester is realized. The invention also provides application of the fucose ester in preparation of personal care products or household cleaning products. The trehalose ester is added into the corresponding product, so that the product performance can be improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种海藻糖酯，为海藻糖与脂肪酸的酯化物的混合物；所述海藻糖酯的组分中含单酯、双酯、三酯，其中单酯含量＞40%，最高可达70%以上；所述脂肪酸例如可以为C6‑C24的脂肪酸或其混合物，优选C12脂肪酸含量≥50%，最优选C12脂肪酸含量≥70%。本发明采用无溶剂法以及酯交换合成路线，选取毒性较低的碳酸钾和硬脂酸钠作为催化剂和分散剂，并结合乙酸乙酯/乙醇分离体系，活性炭/过氧化氢乙醇脱色体系，开发出一种单酯含量高，可工业化的低成本的海藻糖酯的无溶剂法制备方法。本发明还提供了一种藻糖酯在制备个人护理产品或家庭清洁产品中的应用。通过将海藻糖酯加入对应的产品中，可以提高产品性能。"
                }
            ]
